{"title":"众口齐夸五老村（车灯调）","authors":["曾田家"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":10,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"众口齐夸五老村（车灯调）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾田家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南京市，五老村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这条街道很有名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫生工作成绩大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲等模范远近闻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽宽马路随游逛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路面整洁无灰尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂马达轰轰响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学校朗朗读书声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福院里老人把棋下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼儿园孩子咦呀学语好天真。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女个个心舒畅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身强力壮有精神！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五老村是幸福村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少笑盈盈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低头回想当年事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不觉两眼泪淋淋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一首民谣曾描述，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一字一句活生生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年五老村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是个苦恼村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛆成堆，蝇成群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屎球随水滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疫病不离身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚊子碰破脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垃圾污水熏死人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霹雳一声春雷响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷苦百姓大翻身！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家搞清洁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"户户讲卫生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"填平臭水塘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻改土毛坑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬走垃圾堆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路都修平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除四害人人都展劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彻彻底底无蚊蝇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面目一新好光景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众口齐夸五老村！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}